{"tid":769252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聯招放榜】「超級狀元」入港大讀醫 黃子衡即席表演音樂","createTime":"2018-08-06T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T06:23:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6e073e6d6e5079024f575f1dc457357d1de1d56c","tid":769252,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180806/_2018080611432290483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180806%2F_2018080611432290483.jpg&h=dcf0d52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今年中學文憑試（DSE）中，有兩位狀元選擇入讀港大醫學院內外全科醫學士課程。他們分別為考獲9科5*（包括數學延伸部分），堪稱「超級狀元」、來自喇沙書院的黃子衡（Thomas Wong）；和來自拔萃女書院、考獲7科5*的女「狀元」林悅兒（Josie Lam）。<br />\n<br />\n今年入讀內外全科醫學士課程的同學，平均成績（最佳六科）持續在39分以上。排名首30名的考生，平均成績更高達41.27。考獲六科5**或以上的同學，包括兩位「狀元」，共有14名。<br />\n<br />\n今年醫學院亦取錄了多名優異非聯招學生，其中包括14名考獲國際預科文憑課程（IB）45分滿分的尖子學生。<br />\n<br />\n除內外全科醫學士課程外，港大醫學院其他課程收生成績亦再有所提升。入讀生物醫學學士課程和藥劑學學士課程的學生，平均成績（最佳六科）分別為35.833和35.583的佳績。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學李嘉誠醫學院院長梁卓偉今天聯同黃子衡、林悅兒，以及多名IB尖子，包括來自沙田學院的Andrian Chan和Yu Wing Sze、來自拔萃男書院的Ralph Yip、來自德瑞國際學校的Harriet Kwok、來自聖士提反書院的Hugo Leung和Kelvin Tong，和來自漢基國際學校的Samantha Chong會見記者，同學於記者會上暢談感受。黃子衡更即席與梁卓偉教授一起表演音樂，顯示他多才多藝的一面。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉表示，醫學院明年收生有新安排，「鑑於許多聯招同學對港大醫科收生的高門檻有顧慮，有些雖然很有興趣而成績亦很不錯，但因未能肯定自己的機會而裹足不前，十分可惜。因此我們會在今年的入學資訊日清楚公佈明年醫科的收生門檻。同學只要DSE 成績達標，而面試表現良好，我們便會取錄。同學們會在六月內收到面試成績結果，在七月聯招放榜時便可肯定自己會否被取錄」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1283913/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1283913%2F&d=oOZMTXzW7vfu8itstuCjnTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b017f434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1283913%2F&h=1c013e8a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1283913/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170320/b3795ffbc3f44aaa8f3b2748f02561e6_th.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.itc.cn%2Fupload%2F20170320%2Fb3795ffbc3f44aaa8f3b2748f02561e6_th.jpeg&h=b7c609a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35832159bec0fda6a3f3dccde427cedf4e733f3e","tid":769252,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪得今朝係港大站見到佢拎住個大樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bb27fd8c626c05ff9f57a2367c807b06009030","tid":769252,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"上天真係好公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4566eadc405fb86e296bd24f793e962439c5d101","tid":769252,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c526ee5f547c0ef77098ab924db8072c658f16","tid":769252,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"Hku 真係好柒<br />\n咁樣都要開個記者會<br />\n仲要玩埋音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521c04ba3a63efe4da3434192f27bafdbf592803","tid":769252,"uid":99929,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"高分低能仔，大王同佢握手，坐係到遞隻手出黎又唔眼神接觸，香港專出產呢D讀書叻但唔識做人既傻西"},{"pid":"7aed19965e58e0ca74e94701d5a8ee97b45422a7","tid":769252,"uid":2002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"人地做醫生洗撚睇人臉色咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a126cd845c336af610ed8c11526d86d3f9eab8","tid":769252,"uid":105256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}